    <p>Neither Telecommut.com nor any of its agents or affiliates shall be liable for any direct, incidental, consequential, indirect, or punitive damages arising out of user's access, use, or inability to use Telecommut.com web site, or any errors or omissions in the content of Telecommut.com web site.</p>

    <p>Any communication or material you transmit to Telecommut.com web site or internet electronic mail is transmitted by you on a non-confidential basis. Telecommut.com makes no promise, express or implied, not to use such communication or material for any purpose whatsoever, including reproduction, publication, broadcast and posting.</p>

    <br/>
